- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper encodes the problem as a SAT instance.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as SAT solvers are commonly used in AI applications.
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with combinatorial optimization of finite automata.
